caller_intent: Caleb called back to confirm details about his canceled home and auto policy, including the refund amount and timeline, and to clarify his reason for switching providers.
resolution_steps: Brandi confirmed the policy cancellation and asked Caleb about his new provider.
Caleb disclosed he switched due to a lower price.
Brandi verified the refund check details (amount: $2,850.32, sent today, expected arrival in 2 weeks).
Brandi offered to track the refund if it didn't arrive on time.
knowledge_required: Customer communication protocols for policy changes
systems_referenced: Internal insurance agency system for checking refund status
summary: Caleb confirmed his switch to a new provider due to lower pricing. Brandi provided details about his refund check ($2,850.32) and assured him it would arrive within two weeks. The conversation concluded with Caleb expressing gratitude and ending the call.
